\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.87"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)的系数。该算法是
\begin_inset Formula $O\left(n\right)$
\end_inset

复杂度。
\end_layout

